{"about_the_game":"In Drizzlepath you are set on a journey to the top of the Mountain of Fire. This game is what you'd call a &quot;walking simulator&quot;. It aims to be an atmospheric, relaxed and enigmatic experience. It was made in CryEngine 3 to achieve an immersive graphic quality. If you enjoy games that are about the experience of discovering of the world around you, you will probably love Drizzlepath.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhen you download the game, you also have the game's OST in your &quot;...Steam\\steamapps\\common\\Drizzlepath\\Drizzlepath OST&quot; folder.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote: Drizzlepath is a short game and has no save feature. The checkpoint system in game is for situations like getting stuck in a hole or dying by falling down from high grounds. It only works in game session and resets when you quit game to main menu or desktop.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPS: The core aspect of this game is the atmosphere. It is recommended for those who mostly seek to experience the mood.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/355760/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728893182","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/355760/page.bg.jpg?t=1728893182","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/355760/32772ca1ba08c03bbcd3f77b16fd2fe0e8ea8e37/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728893182","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/355760/32772ca1ba08c03bbcd3f77b16fd2fe0e8ea8e37/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728893182","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Trading Cards","id":29},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"In Drizzlepath you are set on a journey to the top of the Mountain of Fire. This game is what you'd call a &quot;walking simulator&qu